mig.core

Class Owned

  • java.lang.Object
    • mig.core.Owned

  • public class Owned
extends java.lang.Object
    Owned is the class that contains the bunch, the inventory and the notebook

    Owned contains these elements:

    • A bunch of keys
    • A notebook which contains information
    • An inventory which contains Physical Object.

    This class refuse object(key, information, PhysicalObject) in double in its ArrayList

    Version:
    20/11/2016
    Author:
    Group8
    See Also:
    Key, Information, PhysicalObject
